            Nikole Vannest
          
          
            
              I am a master’s candidate at the University of
              California - Santa Barbara’s Bren School for Environmental
              Science and Management, currently residing in Santa
              Barbara, CA. I’m interested in using environmental data to
              better understand forested and terrestrial ecosystems
              through modeling and creating compelling visuals.
              I also love talking about gardening, travel and
              cooking.
